data.description: Great house approximately 1 mile from Mega Boat Landing being constructed in Moncks Corner. Large family room, spacious kitchen, and a half acre yard. This home is the perfect place to settle in and get acquainted with the Low Country. Three bedrooms on the main floor with a bonus bedroom above the garage recently renovated. The backyard is fully fenced and has a large screened in back porch and a deck to watch the sunset. This house is perfect for a buyer wanting to customize it to their own space. Buyer to verify all information, measurements, and condition of property.
